text:
Dübendorf is a municipality in the district of Uster in the canton of Zurich in Switzerland.
It is a suburb of Zürich with a population of about 26,000 (2014). It is the fourth largest city in the canton, after Zürich, Winterthur and Uster.
Villages.
Dübendorf, Dübelstein, Geeren, Gfenn, Gockhausen, Hermikon and Stettbach.
